# Communication

- Reference existing code with Cursor code citations: a fenced block whose info string is `startLine:endLine:filepath` (opening fence alone on its line).
- When citing paths or `https://` URLs, use the full string; do not shorten for brevity.
- Prefer markdown links for web references. Write in complete sentences; avoid telegraphic shorthand.
